<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>SETR — AI Appointment Setting for Insurance Agents</title>
<meta name="description" content="SETR is an AI-powered appointment-setting platform for insurance agents. Sign up to receive product information, demo scheduling, and follow-up communications.">
<style>
  @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Oswald:wght@500;600;700&family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700&display=swap');
  :root{
    --bg:#0a0a0a;--card:#131313;--field:#1c1c1c;--field-border:#2a2a2a;
    --accent:#a3e635;--text:#f4f4f4;--muted:#8a8a8a;--faint:#5a5a5a;
  }
  *{box-sizing:border-box;margin:0;padding:0}
  body{background:var(--bg);font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;color:var(--text);line-height:1.6}
  a{color:var(--accent)}
  .wrap{max-width:680px;margin:0 auto;padding:0 20px}

  header{border-bottom:1px solid #1e1e1e}
  .nav{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;padding:22px 0;max-width:680px;margin:0 auto;padding-left:20px;padding-right:20px}
  .brand{font-family:'Oswald',sans-serif;font-weight:700;font-size:24px;letter-spacing:.5px;color:var(--accent);text-transform:lowercase}
  .nav a.help{font-size:13px;font-weight:600;color:var(--muted);text-decoration:none}

  .hero{padding:54px 0 10px}
  .eyebrow{font-size:12px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:2px;color:var(--accent);text-transform:uppercase;margin-bottom:16px}
  h1{font-family:'Oswald',sans-serif;font-weight:700;font-size:46px;line-height:1.08;letter-spacing:-.5px;margin-bottom:18px}
  .subhead{font-size:16px;color:var(--muted);max-width:540px}

  .card{background:var(--card);border:1px solid #1e1e1e;border-radius:16px;padding:36px 40px;margin:36px 0}
  .row{display:flex;gap:16px}
  .row .field{flex:1}
  .field{margin-bottom:20px}
  label{display:block;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:1.5px;color:var(--muted);text-transform:uppercase;margin-bottom:9px}
  input{width:100%;background:var(--field);border:1px solid var(--field-border);border-radius:8px;padding:14px 16px;color:var(--text);font-size:15px;font-family:'Inter',sans-serif}
  input::placeholder{color:var(--faint)}
  input:focus{outline:none;border-color:var(--accent)}

  .consent{border:1px solid var(--field-border);border-radius:10px;padding:18px 20px;display:flex;gap:14px;margin:6px 0 26px}
  .consent input[type=checkbox]{appearance:none;width:18px;height:18px;min-width:18px;margin-top:2px;border:1px solid #3a3a3a;border-radius:4px;background:#fff;cursor:pointer;position:relative}
  .consent input[type=checkbox]:checked{background:var(--accent);border-color:var(--accent)}
  .consent input[type=checkbox]:checked::after{content:"";position:absolute;left:5px;top:1px;width:5px;height:10px;border:solid #0a0a0a;border-width:0 2px 2px 0;transform:rotate(45deg)}
  .consent-text{font-size:12px;line-height:1.7;color:var(--muted)}
  .consent-text strong{color:var(--text);font-weight:700}
  .tag{display:inline-block;background:var(--accent);color:#0a0a0a;font-size:10px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:.5px;padding:2px 7px;border-radius:4px;margin-right:6px;text-transform:uppercase}

  .cta{width:100%;background:var(--accent);color:#0a0a0a;border:none;border-radius:10px;padding:18px;font-family:'Oswald',sans-serif;font-size:16px;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:1.5px;text-transform:uppercase;cursor:pointer;transition:background .15s}
  .cta:hover{background:#b6f04a}
  .footnote{text-align:center;font-size:12px;color:var(--faint);margin-top:16px}
  .footnote a{color:var(--faint)}

  .info{padding:8px 0 40px}
  .info h2{font-family:'Oswald',sans-serif;font-size:22px;margin-bottom:12px}
  .info p{color:var(--muted);font-size:15px;margin-bottom:14px}
  .info ul{color:var(--muted);font-size:15px;margin:0 0 14px 20px}
  .info li{margin-bottom:6px}

  footer{border-top:1px solid #1e1e1e;padding:28px 0;text-align:center}
  footer .brand{font-size:18px;margin-bottom:10px}
  footer .links a{color:var(--muted);font-size:13px;text-decoration:none;margin:0 10px}
  footer .copy{color:var(--faint);font-size:12px;margin-top:12px}

  @media(max-width:520px){
    .card{padding:28px 22px}
    h1{font-size:34px}
    .row{flex-direction:column;gap:0}
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>
  <header>
    <div class="nav">
      <span class="brand">setr</span>
      <a class="help" href="mailto:support@setrpro.io">support@setrpro.io</a>
    </div>
  </header>

  <main class="wrap">
    <section class="hero">
      <div class="eyebrow">Get Started</div>
      <h1>AI appointment setting<br>for insurance agents.</h1>
      <p class="subhead">SETR books qualified appointments for individual agents and agency teams — automated outreach, follow-up, and scheduling, done for you.</p>
    </section>

    <section class="card" id="signup">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="field">
          <label for="first">First Name</label>
          <input type="text" id="first" name="first" placeholder="Marcus" autocomplete="given-name">
        </div>
        <div class="field">
          <label for="last">Last Name</label>
          <input type="text" id="last" name="last" placeholder="Thompson" autocomplete="family-name">
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="field">
        <label for="email">Email Address</label>
        <input type="email" id="email" name="email" placeholder="you@agency.com" autocomplete="email">
      </div>

      <div class="field">
        <label for="phone">Mobile Phone Number</label>
        <input type="tel" id="phone" name="phone" placeholder="(904) 555-0100" autocomplete="tel">
      </div>

      <div class="consent">
        <input type="checkbox" id="consent" name="consent">
        <label for="consent" class="consent-text">
          <span class="tag">Optional</span>I consent to receive SMS messages from <strong>SETR LLC</strong> regarding the SETR platform, including product information, demo scheduling, and follow-up communications. Message &amp; data rates may apply. Message frequency varies. Reply <strong>STOP</strong> to cancel. Reply <strong>HELP</strong> for help. <strong>This consent is not required as a condition of receiving any service or making a purchase.</strong>
        </label>
      </div>

      <button class="cta" type="button">Get Started &nbsp;&rarr;</button>

      <p class="footnote">
        No credit card required · No spam, ever.<br>
        By submitting, you agree to our <a href="terms.html">Terms &amp; Conditions</a> and <a href="privacy.html">Privacy Policy</a>.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="info">
      <h2>About SETR</h2>
      <p>SETR is an AI-powered appointment-setting platform built for insurance agents and agency teams. The platform contacts your leads, qualifies them, handles follow-up, and schedules appointments directly onto your calendar.</p>
      <h2 style="margin-top:24px">Messaging &amp; consent</h2>
      <p>By submitting the form above and checking the consent box, you agree to receive SMS messages from SETR LLC related to the SETR platform — including product information, demo scheduling, and follow-up communications.</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Message frequency varies.</li>
        <li>Message and data rates may apply.</li>
        <li>Reply <strong>STOP</strong> at any time to opt out.</li>
        <li>Reply <strong>HELP</strong> for assistance, or email support@setrpro.io.</li>
        <li>Consent is not a condition of purchase.</li>
      </ul>
      <p>For details on how we handle your information, see our <a href="privacy.html">Privacy Policy</a> and <a href="terms.html">Terms &amp; Conditions</a>.</p>
    </section>
  </main>

  <footer>
    <div class="wrap">
      <div class="brand">setr</div>
      <div class="links">
        <a href="privacy.html">Privacy</a>
        <a href="terms.html">Terms</a>
        <a href="mailto:support@setrpro.io">Contact</a>
      </div>
      <div class="copy">© 2026 SETR LLC · All rights reserved.</div>
    </div>
  </footer>
</body>
</html>
